snippet.title: Freddi Fish 2: The Case of The Haunted Schoolhouse Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Freddi Fish 2: The Case of The Haunted Schoolhouse Full Playthrough

Freddi Fish 2: The Case of The Haunted Schoolhouse is a game created by Humongous Entertaiment in 1996. In this game, a ghost is haunting the schoolhouse and its stealing the little guppies' toys. You must help Freddi and Luther set up a trap for the ghosts, who turn out to be sharks.
